data.description:
The seller has an assumable VA loan that you can assume at 5.25% and willing to give $3,500 towards buyers concessions!!

Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Ocean Springs! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom, 2-story house offers a spacious and comfortable living environment, boasting 2,305 square feet of well-designed living space. Nestled in a community known for its award-winning schools, this property is perfect for families seeking both quality education and a beautiful place to call home.

As you approach the property, you'll be captivated by its charming curb appeal and manicured landscaping. The fenced yard not only provides privacy but also ensures a safe and secure space for outdoor activities. Additionally, a convenient shed is included with the property, offering extra storage space for your gardening tools and outdoor equipment.

Step inside, and you'll discover an open floorplan on the main level that is perfect for entertaining family and friends. The spacious living area seamlessly connects to the dining room and kitchen, creating a welcoming and inclusive atmosphere for gatherings. The modern kitchen features updated appliances, ample counter space, and a center island, making it a chef's delight.

Venture upstairs to find all four bedrooms, including a huge master suite that will leave you in awe. The master bedroom is a sanctuary of comfort, offering generous space and natural light. The en-suite bathroom is equally impressive, featuring double vanities, a luxurious soaking tub, a separate shower, and a walk-in closet, providing a private retreat for relaxation.

The remaining three bedrooms are well-appointed and share a stylishly appointed full bathroom. With plenty of space for everyone, this home ensures both comfort and convenience for your family's needs.

Located in the vibrant community of Ocean Springs, you'll have easy access to a variety of amenities, including shops, restaurants, parks, and more. The award-winning schools in the area make this home an ideal choice for families looking to provide their children with a top-notch education.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom, 2-story house your forever home. With its thoughtful design, spacious layout, and excellent location, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Schedule a viewing today and prepare to fall in love with your future home in Ocean Springs!

The seller has an assumable VA loan that you can assume at 5.25%!!
